items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 320 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 65!

items.checkin_comment: Massive hop bill, and a huge fruit concoction to match. It is a great beer.

items.badge_description: Lovers of little green cones rejoice. National IPA Day is pretty much like your best birthday! Whether you love hazies, milkshake, double, triple, or even quad IPAs just check in one today to earn this coveted badge.

A global celebration of beer, International Beer Day toasts to beers from all across the globe. Like a helles from Germany, a tripel from Belgian, or an ESB from Britain. Cheers to you, wherever you might be in the world!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 355 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 72!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 300 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 61! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

user.bio: Craft beer nut. Aim it to drink 2000 different craft beers before I hit 50.

Beer explorer. Likes dark sours, brett, spon ferm, abbey ales, barrel-aged and anything with innovative flavors.
Bell curve believer. 1=garbage, 2=wont have again, 3=good brew, 4=recommended, 5=the BEST. ABV & price matter.
